        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47. \r\rYour target is Umberto Megazzini, a beloved childrens&apos; entertainer with a dark secret. Over the past decade, Megazzini has left a trail of grisly murder and rape that rivals the likes of Dahmer and Chikatilo. Of course, no one suspects the beloved Fool of Sapienza to be capable of more than humorous gags. Our client, a woman who narrowly survived Megazzini&apos;s deadly obsessions, has hired us to do what the law cannot.\r\rHappy hunting, 47.",
